### ============================================================
### FembStockTicker — HTTP Request Tests
### VS Code: install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
### JetBrains: built-in HTTP Client support
###
### Fill in the Auth0 variables below before running
### authenticated requests.
### ============================================================

@host = http://localhost:7236

# Auth0 credentials — fill in from your Auth0 dashboard
@auth0_domain    = dev-0a51rold.au.auth0.com
@auth0_client_id     = YOUR_CLIENT_ID
@auth0_client_secret = YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET
@auth0_audience      = YOUR_API_AUDIENCE

### ============================================================
### [1] Fetch Auth0 Token (Machine-to-Machine / Client Credentials)
###     Run this first, then use {{auth_response.response.body.access_token}}
###     in the requests below (VS Code REST Client auto-captures it).
### ============================================================

# @name auth_response
POST https://{{auth0_domain}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client_id": "{{auth0_client_id}}",
  "client_secret": "{{auth0_client_secret}}",
  "audience": "{{auth0_audience}}",
  "grant_type": "client_credentials"
}

###

### ============================================================
### [2] GET /api/weatherforecast — No token (expect 401)
### ============================================================

GET {{host}}/api/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### [3] GET /api/weatherforecast — Authenticated, default (5 days)
### ============================================================

GET {{host}}/api/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_response.response.body.access_token}}

###

### ============================================================
### [4] GET /api/weatherforecast?days=3 — Authenticated, 3 days
### ============================================================

GET {{host}}/api/weatherforecast?days=3
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_response.response.body.access_token}}

###

### ============================================================
### [5] GET /api/weatherforecast?days=10 — Authenticated, 10 days
### ============================================================

GET {{host}}/api/weatherforecast?days=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_response.response.body.access_token}}

###

### ============================================================
### [6] GET /api/weatherforecast — Tampered token (expect 401)
### ============================================================

GET {{host}}/api/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer this.is.not.a.valid.token

###
